sonusPerformanceStatisticsMIB.description: The MIB module to describe Sonus Performance Statistics objects.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalSize.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalSize
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalSize.description: The size of the intervals in minutes for the Sonus Trunk Group interval table.

sonusTrunkGroupNumberOfIntervals.name: sonusTrunkGroupNumberOfIntervals
sonusTrunkGroupNumberOfIntervals.description: The number of intervals for the Sonus Trunk Group interval table. The sonusTrunkGroupIntervalSize times the sonusTrunkGroupNumberOfIntervals must be <= 1440.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentTable.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentTable
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentTable.description: The Sonus Trunk Group Current table.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentEntry.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentEntry
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentEntry.description: An entry in the Sonus Trunk Group Current table.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInUsage.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInUsage
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInUsage.description: The current usage in the inbound direction for this trunk group. Usage is defined as the time a trunk is seized to the time it is released.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutUsage.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutUsage
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutUsage.description: The current usage in the outbound direction for this trunk group. Usage is defined as the time a trunk is seized to the time it is released.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCalls.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCalls
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCalls.description: The current number of completed inbound calls on this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCalls.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCalls
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCalls.description: The current number of completed outbound calls on this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallAttempts.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallAttempts
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallAttempts.description: The current number of inbound call attempts on this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallAttempts.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallAttempts
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallAttempts.description: The current number of outbound call attempts on this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentMaxCompletedCalls.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentMaxCompletedCalls
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentMaxCompletedCalls.description: The current maximum number of completed calls in the inbound and outbound direction for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentCallSetupTime.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentCallSetupTime
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentCallSetupTime.description: The current total call setup time for all completed calls in the inbound and outbound directions for this trunk group measured in hundredths of a second. This object can be used as the numerator for calculating average call setup time.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentCallSetups.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentCallSetups
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentCallSetups.description: The current total number of calls setup but not necessarily completed in the inbound and outbound directions for this trunk group. This object can be used as the denominator for calculating average call setup time.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoRoutes.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoRoutes
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoRoutes.description: The current number of inbound failed calls because there was no route available for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoResour.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoResources
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoResour.description: The current number of inbound failed calls because there was an unavailable resource for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoServic.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoService
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNoServic.description: The current number of inbound failed calls because there was an unavailable service for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailInvalidC.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailInvalidCall
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailInvalidC.description: The current number of inbound failed calls because there was an invalid call attempt for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNetworkF.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNetworkFailure
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailNetworkF.description: The current number of inbound failed calls because there was a network failure for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailProtocol.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailProtocolError
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailProtocol.description: The current number of inbound failed calls because there was a protocol error for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailUnspecif.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailUnspecified
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentInCallFailUnspecif.description: The current number of inbound failed calls for an unspecified reason for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoRoute.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoRoutes
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoRoute.description: The current number of outbound failed calls because there was no route available for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoResou.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoResources
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoResou.description: The current number of outbound failed calls because there was an unavailable resource for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoServi.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoService
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNoServi.description: The current number of outbound failed calls because there was an unavailable service for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailInvalid.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailInvalidCall
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailInvalid.description: The current number of outbound failed calls because there was an invalid call attempt for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNetwork.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNetworkFailure
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailNetwork.description: The current number of outbound failed calls because there was a network failure for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailProtoco.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailProtocolError
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailProtoco.description: The current number of outbound failed calls because there was a protocol error for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailUnspeci.name: sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailUnspecified
sonusTrunkGroupCurrentOutCallFailUnspeci.description: The current number of outbound failed calls for an unspecified reason for this trunk group.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalTable.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalTable
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalTable.description: The Sonus Trunk Group Interval table.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalEntry.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalEntry
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalEntry.description: An entry in the Sonus Trunk Group Interval table.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalNumber.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalNumber
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalNumber.description: A number between 1 and 288, which identifies the interval for which the set of statistics is available. The interval identified by 1 is the most recently completed interval, and the interval identified by N is the interval immediately preceding the one identified by N-1.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInUsage.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInUsage
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInUsage.description: The usage in the inbound direction for this trunk group for the specified interval. Usage is defined as the time a trunk is seized to the time it is released.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutUsage.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutUsage
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutUsage.description: The usage in the outbound direction for this trunk group for the specified interval. Usage is defined as the time a trunk is seized to the time it is released.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCalls.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCalls
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCalls.description: The number of completed inbound calls on this trunk group for the specified interval.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCalls.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCalls
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCalls.description: The number of completed outbound calls on this trunk group for the specified interval.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCallAttempts.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCallAttempts
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCallAttempts.description: The number of inbound call attempts on this trunk group for the specified interval.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallAttempts.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallAttempts
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallAttempts.description: The number of outbound call attempts on this trunk group for the specified interval.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalMaxCompletedCalls.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalMaxCompletedCalls
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalMaxCompletedCalls.description: The maximum number of completed calls in the inbound and outbound direction for this trunk group for the specified interval.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalCallSetupTime.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalCallSetupTime
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalCallSetupTime.description: The total call setup time for all completed calls in the inbound and outbound directions for this trunk group for the specified interval measured in hundredths of a second. This object can be used as the numerator for calculating average call setup time.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalCallSetups.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalCallSetups
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalCallSetups.description: The total number of calls setup but not necessarily completed in the inbound and outbound directions for this trunk group for the specified interval. This object can be used as the denominator for calculating average call setup time.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCallFailProtoco.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCallFailProtocolError

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCallFailUnspeci.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalInCallFailUnspecified

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallFailProtoc.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallFailProtocolError

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallFailUnspec.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallFailUnspecified
sonusTrunkGroupIntervalOutCallFailUnspec.description: The number of outbound failed calls for an unspecified reason for this trunk group for the specified interval.

sonusTrunkGroupIntervalTime.name: sonusTrunkGroupIntervalTime
